

                            Angular -(local host:4200)

                        project creation syntax : ng new project_name --routing

                        project run : ng serve --open

                        component creation : syntax : ng g c component_name

                        service creation : syntax : ng g s service_name

                        Directive creation : syntax : ng g d directive_name






                                    Angular Concepts


                        1.component - {html, css ,ts}- Root component - AppComponent

                        2. Module - Root Module - AppModule

                        3. Data Binding

                            3.1 One Way Binding

                                3.1.1 component to view

                                    3.1.1.1 String Interpolation : syntax -{{expression}}

                                    3.1.1.2 Property Binding - syntax : [binding target]="binding source"

                                3.1.2 View to Component

                                    3.1.2.1 Event Binding - syntax: (event-name)="function call"

                                    3.1.2.1 Event Binding using $event- syntax: (event-name)="function ($event)"

                                    3.1.2.3 Template reference variable - syntax : #variable_name
                            
                            
                            3.2  Two Way Binding- FormsModule import -[(ngModel)]="variable_name"
                        
                        4. Angular routing

                        5. Dependency Injection- In constructor 
                        syntax -( access specifies variable_name : dependent class name)

                        6. Angular Services

                        7. ngSubmit - use inside form tag ,  remove event from button tag and change type of button as submit

                        8. Angular Forms

                                8.1 Template driven Forms

                                8.2 Model driven Forms

                                    8.2.1 Reactive Forms -To add Validations-{Add ReactiveFormsModule in app Module}

                                    {Form Group,Form Array, }
                        
